Experiment 1: Hello World Application

 Aim
To develop a simple Android application that displays "Hello World" on the screen.

 Algorithm
1. Start the Android Studio.
2. Create a new Android project.
3. Open activity_main.xml file.
4. Add a TextView to display the text.
5. Write "Hello World!" in the TextView.
6. Run the application.
7. The text "Hello World!" will appear on the screen.
